Table 2.2 consolidates the six forces into a net opportunity-or-threat classification, which feeds directly into the SWOT inventory of Section 2.6. The pattern is informative: the structural forces, technology, environment, society, favour the venture, while the threats are concentrated in the financial and political domains and are, by design, the forces the venture’s structure is built to absorb.
