2.3.6  Segment Selection and Demand Summary
On the segment-selection question, Re-Tire Lebanon deliberately adopts a single-segment focus in Phase 1, concentrating on the anchor compounder, before broadening to a multiple-segment approach across asphalt and sports surfacing from Phase 2. A mass-market approach is explicitly rejected: at startup scale it would dilute the sales bandwidth required to win any single three-to-six-month qualification cycle, and it would forfeit the depth of relationship that industrial selling rewards. Table 2.4 summarises the demand picture and the phase in which each segment is addressed.
