The TOWS matrix converts the SWOT inventory into four families of strategic action by pairing internal factors with external ones, as set out in Table 2.10. Each pairing yields a concrete move rather than an observation, and each is carried forward into the business model refinement of Chapter III or the risk treatment of Chapter IX.
